# Add Letterbox CV
Add a letterbox to the video and scale it to the specified size.  
Note: this program does not support audio.

## Usage
```
usage: addletterboxcv [-h] --dimension WIDTH HEIGHT
                   [--interpolation {NEAREST,LINEAR,AREA,CUBIC,LANCZOS4}]
                   [--codec CODEC]
                   video output
```

